data.description: Beautiful one story, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, open floor plan, freshly painted inside (2023), Granite Countertops, laminate flooring, New hot water heater, AC (inside and outside unit), and New Roof 2022. Dishwasher, garbage disposal, stove, sinks, ceiling fan, blinds, Refrigerator, security system, garage door opener, NEW fencing 2022 with oversized backyard, and Covered Patio. Ready for quick move-in.  This home is very convenient to RAFB, Ft Sam Houston, IH 35, 1604, & The Forum Shopping Center.   Schedule your showing before this one is under contract..
